settings.title: Master of design - 31 years  of experience
Customize the house till its just right for you and your family
Buy direct from the one of America's trusted designers
29+ Years History & Award Winning Plans
settings.text: Our home plans are trusted by new home buyers and builders alike. Expect amazing service, high-quality home plans, reliable turnaround times & trust in our 29+ years of house floor plan design experience.

settings.title: Customize  Your Plan
settings.text: Hire Michael W. Garrell, an award winning designer, directly for best-in-class designs and custom modifications.

settings.title: Low price Guarantee
settings.text: By shopping directly with the original designers, you are ensured the best floor plan purchase price. If you find our plans or a similar plan for sale elsewhere with a better price, we will match it and give you an additional 10% off the matched price.

settings.heading: Need a change ?
settings.subheading: Our team can quickly modify any of our plans to match your needs OR even design one from scratch!

settings.content: In working with Garrell Associates, it feeds into my wife's and I vision of what we wanted for our forever home. We would not only work with Garrell Associates again, we would recommend that anybody out there looking for a home plan or a custom home plan with would with Garrell Associates. They have been wonderful to work with.
settings.author: John Rippie

settings.content: We've purchased 2 different plans from Garrell and couldn't be happier. We asked that one set be reversed and that was handled easily. Both homes we built came out beautifully. What was really nice is that the plans can actually be built as drawn. We seen plans from other companies that included architectural details that were un workable or wouldn't meet code. I'd heartily recommend Garrell Associates.
settings.author: Gregg Heath

settings.content:
Garrell stands out from other designers in that ALL of their plans are aesthetically pleasing to the eye.  They have great floor plans that you can use as-is or tweak to your needs.  No wasted space or undefined uses for rooms.  That's what drew me to them in the first place.  Other house designs that I looked at online had very questionable layouts. Some were just a collection of boxes they called rooms and many just didn't seem to flow right. Garrell plans have a good flow to them.

I have built two houses with Garrell plans.  Both were different designs and each turned out beautifully.  One was a traditional house and my current one is a mountain house.

I built my latest Garrell house on top of a mountain.  I've attached a couple of photos to show you the quality and how it turned out. My wife and I are really pleased with the result.
settings.author: David Sampson

settings.testimonial_Heading: Our 5 Star Reviews speak for themselves
